{
  "stem": "10272.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I didn't get there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just get off the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're heading toward the hospital on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people go by, and they punch me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They saw a Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They come straight over, and they punch me up and curse me on the street.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the, the guard wouldn't go and protect me at that time already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, almost-- we are there at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, there was an air-raid siren.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people start running from the buses and from the-- from the cars, leaving everything on the street and running to a-- to a shelter underground, looking for shelters.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my Ustase, my guard, also was running for it and says, come with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the crowd was so big that I got-- I got lost.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't see him already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I go with the crowd.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The crowd is running to-- they must go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was going with this crowd to a place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They went down into a shelter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was going after them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And  I find myself in, in underground in a shelter in a dark place filled with people sitting next to me, sitting-- somebody with a gun in his hand.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I looked-- after I got used to the darkness already, I could-- I could make out that this is a German-- a German, with a uniform and a gun.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I took off, off slowly this yellow band from me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he saw that I take off this yellow band.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said to me-- he started cursing Hitler, the German, when, when, when this-- when it was-- we heard these detonations, these explosions in the city because the, the, the Americans obviously was bombing somewhere.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
